s the {{wp|Roly-poly toy|type of Daruma doll that does not tip over}}. Its {{t|Fire}} type may be based upon the traditional {{wp|Daruma doll#Daruma burning|Daruma burning ceremony}}.\n\n====Name origin====\nDarumaka and Darumakka seem to be a combination of \'\'{{wp|Daruma doll|Daruma}}\'\' and 真赤 \'\'makka\'\' (crimson) or a corruption of \'\'{{wp|macaque}}\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Fire|type2=Fire\n|ja=ダルマッカ \'\'Darumakka\'\'|jameaning=From \'\'{{wp|Daruma doll|Daruma}}\'\' and {{tt|真赤 \'\'makka\'\'|crimson}} or a corruption of \'\'{{wp|macaque}}\'\'\n|de=Flampion|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Flamme|flame}}\'\' and \'\'{{wp|Paper lantern|{{tt|Lampion|paper lantern}}}}\'\'\n|fr=Darumarond|frmeaning=From \'\'Daruma\'\' and \'\'{{tt|rond|round}}\'\'\n|es=Darumaka|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|it=Darumaka|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=달막화 \'\'Dalmakhwa\'\'|komeaning=From \'\'Daruma\'\' and {{tt|화 (火) \'\'hwa\'\'|fire}}\n|zh_cmn=火紅不倒翁 / 火红不倒翁 \'\'Huǒhóngbùdǎowēng\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|火 \'\'huǒ\'\'|fire}}, {{tt|紅 \'\'hóng\'\'|red}}, {{tt|火紅 \'\'huǒhóng\'\'|blazing}}, and {{wp|roly-poly toy|{{tt|不倒翁 \'\'bùdǎowēng\'\'|tumbler}}}}\n|ru=Дарумака \'\'Darumaka\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n<!--\n==Notes==\n<references />-->\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Fire}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Fire|prevnum=553|prev=Krookodile|nextnum=555|next=Darmanitan}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Flampion]]\n[[es:Darumaka]]\n[[fr:Darumarond]]\n[[it:Darumaka]]\n[[ja:ダルマッカ]]\n[[zh:火红不倒翁]]'}